creator: Droid tech
descriptionHtml:
Best photography application to take super HD highly zoomed photos and videos with Binoculars Model V11 zoom HD Camera. Just open the app and point towards a distant object, stars, moon, sun or small text and drag the zoom scroller. The app will autofocus or you can manually focus.

You can zoom in towards far off objects up to maximum magnification. Take better pictures every time. The app has a launcher button that allows you to launch the camera quickly.

When a picture is captured, a special algorithm enhances the image quality gives it stability if the phone was shaken will taking pictures.

It is built to replace your expensive gadgets like DSLR, Microscope, Telescope, Magnifying Glass, Magnifier, Monocular, Handy Cams, Camcorder, Zoom Cameras, GoPros, and Binoculars.


Features:

- Zooming is possible when shooting

- Turn the torchlight on/off from the application

- Your photo library

- Sharing pictures on Social Networking Application

- Binoculars Model V11

- White balance selector

- Photo and video recording with both front & back cameras

- Supports flashlight

- Various color filters

- Manual focus and autofocus

- Optimized for low light night photography

- Easily switch between front and back cameras

- Easily switch between picture and video recording modes
